{"tid":210823,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《X檔案》再度復活！FOX正式續訂第十一季","createTime":"2017-04-21T08:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T10:16:00.000Z","uid":10626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f304ff2bbd3938a6dd29dbf6ae481cf81eb03910","tid":210823,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/upload/images/thexfiles-again-pic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fimages%2Fthexfiles-again-pic.jpg&h=89624502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經典科幻美劇《X檔案》（The X-Files）於2016年再度重啟播出六集，穆德與史嘉莉這對FBI警探重新回到外星人的世界，試圖揭發人類有史以來最大的陰謀。<br />\n <br />\n此後FOX一直希望能續訂新季，今年一月曾透漏在不久之後就會公布消息，如今終於正式宣布續訂《X檔案》第十一季共十集。主創克里斯卡特（Chris Carter）、吉莉安德森（Gillian Anderson）與大衛杜考夫尼（David Duchovny）已準備就緒，預計今夏開拍，2017年到2018年首播。同時釋出一張主視覺，宣告《X檔案》即將回歸。（screencrush）<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/news/20170421/003.html?utm_source=dramaqueenfb&amp;utm_campaign=dramaqueenfb&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Fnews%2F20170421%2F003.html%3Futm_source%3Ddramaqueenfb%26utm_campaign%3Ddramaqueenfb%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f05ae451\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/news/20170421/003.html?utm_source=dramaqueenfb&amp;utm_campaign=dramaqueenfb&amp;utm_medium=referral</a>"},{"pid":"59109616ebb47f8274118812d8aacc6b295bfa59","tid":210823,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:37:37.000Z","msg":"唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老成咁。"},{"pid":"7786843b40289b19e6894953ddcba48f09427762","tid":210823,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老成咁。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://m.popkey.co/2afece/gKwQ5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht